So pros and cons of sharing a single project like this.

00:13:05.460 --> 00:13:10.659
What's good about it is that students land directly in a project upon login, which means

00:13:10.659 --> 00:13:18.179
they get the URL from you, and what they see is an RStudio ID, and they can get started.

00:13:18.179 --> 00:13:23.340
It works well for workshops where all the work that will be done completed is in a single

