for themselves, they now control the permissions of that project, which means they can simply

00:15:12.900 --> 00:15:17.140
share it with another friend, and if this is an assignment where you don't want students

00:15:17.140 --> 00:15:22.700
sharing code, now you've made it additionally easy for them to do so.

00:15:22.700 --> 00:15:27.859
Obviously, you controlling permissions of a project does not necessarily mean your students

