aren't going to cheat if that's what they really want to do, but I think as instructors,

00:15:33.179 --> 00:15:39.020
it is important for us, if we do want to follow certain rules about sharing work, that we

00:15:39.020 --> 00:15:45.739
don't use a platform that makes it too easy for students to cheat.

00:15:45.739 --> 00:15:51.099
On a remote teaching note, I think one of the things that makes it hardest for sharing

